{"tid":1609300,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[統計] 一句講曬 聽日三唔三罷","createTime":"2019-10-01T14:14:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T18:03:59.000Z","uid":192730,"like":416,"dislike":117,"uniUserReply":75,"replies":[{"pid":"faf45b46fb9dc66c944ea134e570f488a0bf14c0","tid":1609300,"uid":192730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:14:11.000Z","msg":"統計下<br />\n睇下連登手足大致既取向係點<br />\n一句講曬 <br />\n聽日開始無限期三罷 再次遍地開花<br />\n定留力谷落黎緊個星期六日<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講左咁多次升級升級<br />\n唔知幾多個手足被自殺<br />\n係新屋嶺入面比人輪姦 比人酷刑<br />\n如果唔打鐵趁熱既話<br />\n無論你做幾多文宣都好星期日只會同平時既星期日一樣<br />\n對侍 食tg 散 落單被捕<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日三罷都仲要回氣抖幾日先個d失敗主意者<br />\n你對唔對得住中左槍瞓左係醫院生死未卜 仲比人告暴動罪既手足?</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聽日開始罷佢老母 黑警血債血償<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不了 星期六日放假先啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港豬:腦細 今日香港戒嚴 哪有車 你老母 聽日翻唔撚到<br />\n就係咁簡單<br />\n其實有咩要考慮?</span></span>"},{"pid":"9a81abc1bbe9f8c63a11f228d7bd3b805e05cc52","tid":1609300,"uid":192730,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:16:24.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n安全離開左既手足快d入黎幫手推聽日既po<br />\n一定唔可以就咁就罷休"},{"pid":"ca26a53e88eb6adfe3b0b02227dca5b8e32282f1","tid":1609300,"uid":115769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:18:38.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4863524950113584c048bb5938f3723d435fef27","tid":1609300,"uid":63838,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:18:51.000Z","msg":"聽日起碼搞鳩中環先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84149b0742095f40ce89e739256a7601517bbf8a","tid":1609300,"uid":192730,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:19:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">罷工好難<br />\n被罷工好易<br />\n起碼都要多人d投票<br />\n比d打工仔