islike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:33:48.000Z","msg":"幫你推"},{"pid":"c8a7e67ed2e942b9d1c99f2f7a40f70955229901","tid":1609300,"uid":152440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:34:11.000Z","msg":"罷 完"},{"pid":"49a9c5df59e228288c508a1245e0935c7d16e35e","tid":1609300,"uid":64703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:34:48.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70976409cbc62abbde5f485f7ce5b267afed8140","tid":1609300,"uid":305022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:35:26.000Z","msg":"我P牌一日只係開到一個POST，麻煩手足認同請幫開POST<br />\n<br />\n811爆眼812入機場<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n101實彈大鑊過爆眼但係102縮番入老母個閪到？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSORRY我做唔到<br />\n<br />\n單純罷工罷巿係推動唔到大家做，一定要有目標<br />\n<br />\n就算唔係機場都一定要有一個目標<br />\n<br />\n但我唔覺有任何地方比機場好<br />\n<br />\n有無諗過點解罷工攪唔成？因為有得番工既年齡層並唔係感受到前線最深刻痛楚果種階層<br />\n<br />\n你可以話機場送頭，但係唔該比第二個方案<br />\n認同請轉發同埋推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae08f97a6ce6582da109be1c4252dd212247ca2d","tid":1609300,"uid":192730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:35:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"c