9300,"uid":267006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:38:08.000Z","msg":"相信今日大家除左淚水，就只有忿怒。<br />\n我睇左好多好多好多次個學生中槍既片段，真係好心痛。呢件事唔可以就咁就算，一定要推上國際。<br />\n<br />\n我希望大家可以花少少時間send一封email去美國名嘴talk show主持人Stephen Colbert，請求佢係節目入面將香港警察開槍、企圖殺害學生既事公開，令全美國、甚至全世界既觀眾都知道而家香港既人道危機。<br />\n<br />\n以下係template一份，歡迎修改/proof read。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://audienceservices.cbs.com/feedback/feedback.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faudienceservices.cbs.com%2Ffeedback%2Ffeedback.htm&d=JxnAwUrH%2B1qYxVTFfur%2BVkbB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=aa3d1bc3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://audienceservices.cbs.com/feedback/feedback.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n（入到去揀Late Show with Stephen Colbert)<br />\n<br />\nDear Stephen,<br />\n<br />\nWe are a group of Hong Kong audience who appreciate your show very much. Your monologue is always entertaining yet it delivers important messages to the world on righteousness and freedom.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Who kills its own kind on his birthday?&rdquo;<br />\nCHINA.<br />\n<br />\nWe are writing to ask for your help as Hong Kong is now experiencing a serious humanitarian crisis. On 1st October, a HK police officer fired live rounds at a young protester&rsquo;s chest. This protester is a high school student who is currently in ICU with a critical medical condition. Here&rsquo;s the video footage:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/KnAcFz20qAw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FKnAcFz20qAw&d=JxnAwUrH%2B1qYxVTFfur%2BVkbB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=f2329e0f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/KnAcFz20qAw</a><br />\n<br />\nAs you can see clearly from the video, the moment the police officer fired a bullet at the protester&rsquo;s chest, the officer&rsquo;s life was at no risk. The fact that he was marching towards the crowd with his gun pointing at them, instead of stepping backwards proves that he was not self-defending, but aggressive. The shooting was completely unreasonable, violent and brutal. This is undoubtedly a violation of human rights.<br />\n<br />\nHong Kong people need your help to spread the police brutality to the world because there&rsquo;s nothing we can do to sanction these inhuman acts in Hong Kong. Please, you are our last hope. If you believe in freedom, if you believe in justice, if you believe the very basic human rights, please feature this shocking video in your next Late Show with Stephen Colbert.<br />\n<br />\nThank you for your kind attention.<br />\n<br />\nRegards,<br />\nHongkongers"},{"pid":"cbc563b45f7f03e7d3346f6063d00fd57115e875","tid":1609300,"uid":192730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:38:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">當你公司有超過一半人都射左波 你仲會翻工咁on9咩<br />\n就係爭你一個<br />\n1+1&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;2</span></span>"},{"pid":"e030ec06e7459e084b011ddfd5b5aa4e95ed7df8","tid":1609300,"uid":42912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:38:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0c5a019897dd5b1f4ad561fff04e03abdae23a8","tid":1609300,"uid":326380,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0e6337cc9891d241b3670e8b99972d4bf412db16","tid":1609300,"uid":31974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:26:17.000Z","msg":"出黎罷佢老母呀<br />\n<br />\n真槍都開埋都唔罷繼續返工？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:38:44.000Z","msg":"好想被罷工"},{"pid":"4f311e1c977378c02fbe4ae2e122dcf3c8584f9c","tid":1609300,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:38:51.000Z","msg":"得返幾粒鐘點罷"},{"pid":"5425170b7197b80b7363a64e26216e51c9e55d73","tid":1609300,"uid":192730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:40:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日係第一槍 <br />\n你地都唔三罷去話比全世界知幾大件事既話<br />\n就好似tg 水炮車咁<br />\n講下講下 港